Waypoint stack — packaged g4klx digital voice daemons
======================================================

The binary shipped in this package is an unmodified build of an upstream
g4klx (or Waypoint-forked) source tree, pinned to an exact commit. The
package version encodes that commit: a version of the form

    0~git<7-char-sha>+wp<n>

was built from upstream commit <7-char-sha>; the +wp<n> suffix is the
Waypoint packaging revision against that same pin (it increments for
packaging-only changes and resets to wp1 whenever the pin moves).

This package ships the binary and this document only. Configuration files
and systemd units are NOT shipped here — waypointd renders configuration
and manages the daemon units on the host.

